The Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management app provides a detailed view of various subscriber trends that affect revenue, churn, and customer lifetime value. Marketing Managers can quickly track overall subscriber trends, analyze the trends' effects on revenue, and respond with better products and marketing strategies.

Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions where Media Cloud is enabled
